summary: ...OCTAVE SHOWING LITTLE CHANGE IN STRENGTH AT THIS TIME... As of 2:00 PM PDT Wed Oct 01 the center of Octave was located near 12.0, -116.3 with movement NW at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 994 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
